---
// Story 2.6 — the end-of-page pitch-card chrome (AC2, AC4, AC6).
//
// The page's built-in "upgrade moment" (EXPERIENCE.md KF-1): an end-of-page
// recruiting card rendered AFTER <main> as a direct child of <body>, so its
// heading lives OUTSIDE <article> and never perturbs the in-content heading
// outline. A <footer> that is a direct child of <body> exposes the implicit
// `contentinfo` landmark — a NAMED end-of-page region.
//
// Static HTML + scoped CSS only (no `client:*`, no <script>): server-rendered,
// crawlable, JS-free. Reuses the 2.2 --md-* tokens.
//
// Microcopy is verbatim per EXPERIENCE.md Voice and Tone (AC4): the headline
// (curly apostrophes), the body tail with the em-dash (U+2014) before "your
// layout", inline <code>.md</code>, and the "Same file. Your shape." cadence.
//
// Targets (Decisions A/B): CTA → /get ; "Why a markdown web?" → /vision.
// The headline is an <h4> (NEVER an <h1>) so the page keeps its single <h1>.
// Decorative `▣`/`→` glyphs are aria-hidden so accessible names stay exactly
// "Get the Markdown Web client" and "Why a markdown web?".
---

<footer class="pitch-card">
  <h4 class="pitch-headline">You're reading one fixed view. There's a better one.</h4>
  <p class="pitch-body">
    This page is plain markdown, rendered the same for everyone. In the
    <strong>Markdown Web client</strong>, your own AI personality renders every
    <code>.md</code> page <em>your</em> way — your layout, your language, your
    reading level. Same file. Your shape.
  </p>
  <div class="row">
    <a class="get" href="/get"><span aria-hidden="true">▣</span> Get the Markdown Web client</a>
    <a class="why" href="/vision">Why a markdown web?<span aria-hidden="true"> →</span></a>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .pitch-card {
    margin: 24px 0 64px;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--md-border);
    border-radius: 14px; /* rounded.card */
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fbfdff, #f3f7fc);
  }

  .pitch-headline {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--md-ink);
  }

  .pitch-body {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--md-muted);
  }

  .pitch-body code {
    font-family: var(--md-mono);
    font-size: 85%;
    background: var(--md-code-bg);
    padding: 0.2em 0.4em;
    border-radius: var(--md-radius-code);
  }

  .pitch-body strong {
    color: var(--md-fg);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .get {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #ffffff;
    background: var(--md-ink);
    border-radius: 9px; /* rounded.button */
    padding: 9px 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .why {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--md-link);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .why:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
